posting_body: ['1 BR $1,777', '2 BR $3,132', 'APT # 4917A', 'ASK ME ABOUT APT # 4917A', 'BECKY EVANS WITH REMAX INTEGRITY', 'CALL OR TEXT ME ANYTIME!', 'show contact info', '– CELL', 'Few amenities are more appealing than the rooftop lounge area.', 'With skyline views, an outdoor firepit and plenty of seating, this rooftop lounge will soon become your new favorite meet-up spot in downtown Houston.', 'At least, it will be when you’re not relaxing in the resort-style pool, hanging in the lounge or using the on-site golf simulator.', 'Enjoy subtle perks like valet parking, a 24-hour concierge, and additional climate-controlled storage spaces.', 'Be welcomed by very tall, 11’ ceilings, quartz countertops and state-of-the-art stainless steel appliances.', 'Relax in the quiet sanctitude of your garden-style tub and rainfall-style shower.', 'Call for a tour today!', 'APARTMENT AMENITIES INCLUDE:', '•\tElegant quartz countertops with waterfall edge', '•\tCustom wood 48’’ cabinetry with soft close', '•\tStainless steel farmhouse sinks', '•\tStainless KitchenAid appliance package with convection oven & microwave', '•\tCoffered ceilings', '•\tSeparate showers with rainfall heads', '•\tFull-Size Washers and Dryers', '•\tOversized historic windows', '•\tInternet speeds up to 100 mbps', 'COMMUNITY AMENITIES INCLUDE:', '•\tHeated resort style pool', '•\tSocial lounge with demonstration kitchen', '•\tState of the art fitness center with on demand spin/cardio', '•\tPrivate media/theatre room', '•\tOn-site golf simulator', '•\t24 hr concierge', '•\tResident conference room', '•\tPet-Friendly* Community with On-Site Dog Park and Pet Spa', '•\tRooftop Terrace with outdoor fire pits', '•\tGourmet coffee bar', '•\tClub room with poker table, darts, pool table, ping pong', '•\tOutdoor kitchen and gas grills', 'ASK ME ABOUT APT # 4917A', 'BECKY EVANS WITH REMAX INTEGRITY', 'CALL OR TEXT ME ANYTIME!', 'show contact info', '– CELL']
